### Git commits
- Always commit with descriptive message
- Format: "feat: ...", "fix: ...", "chore: ..."
- One logical change per commit

### Never do
- Never delete existing functionality when adding new features
- Never hardcode price IDs (use constants)
- Never use localStorage (not supported in this setup)
- Never skip error handling in async functions
- Never commit broken TypeScript — run tsc check mentally before committing